        <h2>Research</h2>
        <p class="small">Research interests & keywords:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Wave scattering, Bragg resonance, flexural–gravity waves</li>
          <li>Two-layer fluid models, interfacial waves</li>
          <li>Asymptotic analysis, multiple-scale expansions, spectral methods</li>
          <li>Numerical modelling and MATLAB / Python implementations</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Selected projects</h3>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Bragg scattering of flexural–gravity waves</strong> — derivation, asymptotic expansions, and numerical validation.</li>
          <li><strong>Two-layer fluid interfacial dynamics</strong> — analytical solutions and comparison with experiments/numerics.</li>
        </ol>
